88 SECTION 9.
89 Said article is further amended by adding a new Code section to read as follows:
90 "40-14-19.
91 (a) No contract shall be entered into or renewed by a local governing body or law
92 enforcement agency for the enforcement of speeding violations in a school zone through
93 the use of an automated traffic enforcement safety device on or after the effective date of
94 this Code section.
95 (b) This Code section shall stand repealed on July 1, 2026."
96 SECTION 10.
97 (a) Except as otherwise provided for in subsection (b) of this section, this Act shall become
98 effective upon its approval by the Governor or upon its becoming law without such approval.
99 (b) Sections 1 through 8 of this Act shall become effective on July 1, 2026.
100 SECTION 11.
101 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
